Invocation Name: new year resolutions
des:
This skill will provide you with twenty two new year resolutions to start your year afresh, living you a totally transformed person.

These twenty-two new year resolutions are hidden and will only be revealed when you mention any of the numbers between ONE to TWENTY-TWO.

The skill currently has twenty two new year resolutions to choose from. To invoke any of the hidden resolutions, just mention the corresponding numbers.

Enjoy!
